These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
There 5 different types of food: nectarine, zucchini, watermelon, grapefruit, raspberry
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: rugby, sailing, baseball, snowboarding, biathlon
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, ritmeester, old-henry, bluemaster, chaman
House: colonial, farmhouse, victorian, cottage, cape-cod
 1. the cape-cod house is on the right of the victorian house##1
 2. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
 3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the colonial house##1
 4. the person eating watermelon is the person eating watermelon##1
 5. the colonial house is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 6. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
 7. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
 8. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the cottage house##1
 9. the person eating grapefruit is on the far right##1
10. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the victorian house##1
11. the person eating raspberry is between the ritmeester-smoker and the person who's sport is biathlon##2
12. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
13. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Food      | nectarine        | zucchini | raspberry     | watermelon   | grapefruit |
| Sport   | baseball     | sailing      | snowboarding | biathlon   | rugby    |
| Cigar   | bluemaster  | ritmeester     | baccarat | old-henry | chaman  |
| House           | farmhouse | victorian      | cape-cod     | cottage   | colonial     |

