.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: rose, marigold, orchid, lily, aconite
5 different games are played: domino, monopoly, whist, mah-jongg, go
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: september, november, april, march, january
City: colone, berlin, boston, paris, hamburg
 1. the person traveling to hamburg is in the middle##1
 2. the person playing go is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
 3. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 4. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 5. the person traveling to berlin is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person playing go##2
 6. the person traveling to paris is the person who growsmarigold##1
 7. the person playing domino is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in april is the person playing mah-jongg##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
10. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
11. the person who's birthday is in april is the person who growsorchid##1
12. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Flower         | lily | rose | aconite    | marigold  | orchid    |
| Game   | go    | monopoly       | whist      | domino | mah-jongg        |
| Birthday   | january   | november     | september    | march  | april     |
| City     | boston    | berlin | hamburg | paris | colone |

