 1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far left##1
 2. the person who growsrose is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
 3. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the colonial house##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in january is between the dunhill-smoker and the modern house##2
 5. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
 6. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 7. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
 8. the person who growsdahlia is the bolivar-smoker##1
 9. the siglo-smoker is in the middle##1
10. the dunhill-smoker is the person who's birthday is in september##1
11. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
12. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
13. the bolivar-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
