.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-5::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: black, grey, turquise, ivory, ebony
The people use 5 different means of transport: ship, jet-ski, snowmobile, motorbike, taxi
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: february, april, july, may, october
The people have 5 different hobbies: board-games, magic-tricks, baking, card-games, gardening
 1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 3. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 4. the person who likes turquise is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person driving the ship##2
 5. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 6. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 7. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 9. the person who likes grey is on the far right##1
10. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
11. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
12. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
13. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person who likes black##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
| Color   | ivory       | ebony       | black   | turquise      | grey    |
| Transport       | taxi | motorbike        | ship       | snowmobile       | jet-ski |
