 9. the person who growsbellflower is the cape-cod house##1
10. the person who growsmarigold is in the middle##1
11. the owner of the bird is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
12. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |       4       |     5     |
| Pet      | mouse | ferret | turtle   | bird | rat     |
| Flower   | bellflower | dahlia  | marigold    | begonia          | rose |
| Color         | green | lilac  | ivory | mauve    | blue      |
| House     | cape-cod  | palace   | gothic-revival    | modern          | art-deco      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-17::.
