 2. the person who growsorchid is between the person playing mah-jongg and the person who growsazalea##2
 3. the person who's birthday is in april is the person who growsorchid##1
 4. the person playing poker is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
 5. the person playing whist is in the middle##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in april is between the person who growsbegonia and the person eating pomegranate##2
 7. the person eating artichoke is the person who's birthday is in july##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in may is the person eating cabbage##1
 9. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
10. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
11. the person who growsazalea is the person playing canasta##1
