 4. the person who likes red is on the far left##1
 5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the fan dubstep and the person drinking iced-tea##2
 6. the fan dubstep is on the far left##1
 7. the person playing poker is between the person who likes ebony and the person playing canasta##2
 8. the person playing bridge is between the person playing snooker and the person playing backgammon##2
 9. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
10. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the fan jazz##1

