.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
5 different pets are kept: snake, guinea-pig, hamster, dog, horse
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: surfing, tennis, weightlifting, rugby, climbing
5 different games are played: mah-jongg, whist, snooker, backgammon, scrabble
There are 5 different favourite colors: coral, white, ivory, grey, light-blue
 1. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 2. the person who's sport is climbing is between the person who likes grey and the person playing scrabble##2
 3. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
 4. the person who's sport is climbing is the person playing mah-jongg##1
 5. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person who likes light-blue and the person playing snooker##2
 6. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
 7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person playing backgammon##1
 8. the owner of the dog is the person playing whist##1
 9. the person who likes coral is the person playing whist##1
10. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1
11. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
12. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| Pet         | hamster    | horse  | guinea-pig  | snake      | dog |
| Sport   | tennis    | climbing   | rugby | weightlifting | surfing   |
| Game   | snooker | mah-jongg    | scrabble    | backgammon       | whist         |
| Color   | grey  | white | light-blue    | ivory     | coral      |

 